<h2 style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #333333; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600;">
  Password Reset Request
</h2>

<p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;">
  Hi {{name}},
</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;">
  We received a request to reset the password for your account. If you didn't make this request, you can safely ignore this email.
</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 30px 0; color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;">
  To reset your password, click the button below:
</p>

<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td align="center" style="padding: 0 0 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{resetUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 14px 30px; background-color: #4F46E5; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; border-radius: 6px;">
        Reset Password
      </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #999999; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;">
  Or copy and paste this link into your browser:
</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 30px 0; color: #4F46E5; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; word-break: break-all;">
  {{resetUrl}}
</p>

<div style="background-color: #fef2f2; border-left: 4px solid #ef4444; padding: 15px; margin: 30px 0;">
  <p style="margin: 0; color: #991b1b; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">
    Important Security Information
  </p>
  <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #7f1d1d; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;">
    This link will expire in {{#if expirationHours}}{{expirationHours}} hours{{else}}24 hours{{/if}}. 
    For security reasons, you can only use this link once.
  </p>
</div>

{{#if ipAddress}}
<div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 6px; padding: 20px; margin: 30px 0;">
  <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #666666; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">
    Request Details:
  </p>
  <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #666666; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;">
    <li>Time: {{formatDate requestTime}} at {{formatTime requestTime}}</li>
    {{#if ipAddress}}<li>IP Address: {{ipAddress}}</li>{{/if}}
    {{#if browser}}<li>Browser: {{browser}}</li>{{/if}}
    {{#if location}}<li>Location: {{location}}</li>{{/if}}
  </ul>
</div>
{{/if}}

<p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;">
  If you didn't request a password reset, please let us know immediately by replying to this email or contacting our support team.
</p>

{{#if supportEmail}}
<p style="margin: 0; color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;">
  Need help? Contact us at 
  <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #4F46E5; text-decoration: none;">{{supportEmail}}</a>
</p>
{{/if}}

<p style="margin: 20px 0 0 0; color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;">
  Best regards,<br>
  {{#if teamName}}{{teamName}}{{else}}The Security Team{{/if}}
</p>